  HAL is dead, bug #313393

*razertool-0.0.7-r1 (07 Dec 2009)

  07 Dec 2009; Bernard Cafarelli <voyageur@gentoo.org>
  -razertool-0.0.7.ebuild, +razertool-0.0.7-r1.ebuild:
